data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 1 acre lot, this country ranch style home offers the perfect blend of space, comfort & modern amenities. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms & the main floor laundry room. With nearly 3,000 sq ft of living space, this home provides room for all your needs, whether it's for family gatherings, entertaining friends, or finding your own sanctuary. Custom kitchen/dinette with shiplap walls, features portable dishwasher within a moveable island & newer stainless steel appliances. Recent updates include new shingles, windows, a well, ensuring peace of mind & energy efficiency. Also offers the convenience of a spacious mudroom with a large walk-in pantry, keeping your living spaces organized. The lower level boasts an expansive family room, perfect for cozy evenings or movie nights. Discover 3 additional large bonus rooms with egress windows that can serve as bedrooms, home offices or flex space to suit your lifestyle. The sprawling yard provides endless possibilities, whether you dream of a garden, a playground or simply a peaceful retreat. This property is a true gem.
